main event: Multiple visual sightings of unidentified aerial objects occurred in Miami, Florida on May 5, 1959.
interesting points: The objects were reported to be round or oval-shaped and metallic in appearance., The sightings occurred between 1900L and 2000L., Observers noted several unusual flight characteristics of the objects., A different report mentions a luminous white-green object that was 6 to 7 feet tall., There was a concern for confidentiality as one witness requested the report to be classified.
